Hey "synthetix"; near the top of the page in a brown background it says "Jordan Maxwell - The Naked Truth.avi". 
Just below that it says "Spoken Languages" (English). I hope this is of help to you :P
This is a great torrent. Thanks to the uploader.

Yes, it's in English. It's a 1991 documentary and you can see where Zeitgeist the movie got their material from. If you type Jordan Maxwell The Naked Truth into google you find numerous debunking site/videos to counter this documentary. I thought it was interesting but you really need to see the debunk videos to make a informed judgment.
